- "bloomed" refers to performed;
- "grades" refers to GPAs;
- "average ratings" are the ratings given by students in course evaluations;
- "7th semester" is the specific semester being considered;
- "subjects they are studying" refers to the courses they are enrolled in;
- "department they belong to" refers to the department offering the program.

- "average ratings of the courses" refers to the mean of all course ratings given by students;
